  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddEquation
    This class is responsible for creating the UI components for adding new Equation objects to an existing Brique object.
    AddModel  
    AddNewEquation
    This class creates a dialog for manipulating Equation objects, The first constructor creates a new Equation object, the second constructor allows the user to modify an already existent Equation object.
    AddNewGlobalEquation
    Class responsible for creating the controls to add an equation to the current project, or to modify an already added Equation.
    AddParameter
    This class is responsible for creating the UI components for modifying Equation contents.
